                  "P-LI7"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Neutrons were produced by bombarding a thick",
                "7Li target with a proton beam whose energy Ep=1.912 MeV",
                "is above the reaction threshold of the 7Li(p,n)7Be.",
                "The thick 7Li target as prepared by evaporating",
                "metallic Li on a Pt plate in a Cu target assembly",
                "which has 10 mm diam. The target was cooled by an",
                "air-jet during the experiment."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The 14N sample was a thin melamine film (C3H6N6)",
                "prepared by vacuum evaporation on a 0.01 mm thick",
                "Al foil. From weight of the sample, its thickness was",
                "determined to 212+-1.2mu-g/cm2."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": null,
