              },
              "free_text": [
                " To measure the neutron",
                "flux on the melamine sample, it was replaced with a",
                "6LiF film which was evaporated on an Al foil",
                " (0.01 mm) and 289+-1.2mu-g/cm2 thick.",
                "An unevaporated Al foil was used for background",
                "measurement."
              ]
            }
          ],
